snippet.title: Elli - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Guide Elli on her journey through the land of the Mandragora to reclaim the stolen Crystals of Time before her birthday is over, in this colourful puzzle platformer!

Elli is Available Now! https://goo.gl/HNeg3X
